            <p>Share tasks and communicate effectively with your team to achieve goals faster and more efficiently.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="line"></div>
  
    <div class="content-section">
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Organize and Track Your Tasks</h1>
            <p>Boost your productivity with an easy-to-use task management system.</p>
        </div>
        <img src="https://fellow.app/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/workflow-management.jpg" alt="Progress Tracking">
    </div>

